---
/**
 * Footer — Abogados en CDMX
 * NAP visible in prose for LLMs · Internal links to all SILO nodes
 */
---
<footer class="footer" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer__grid">
      <!-- Col 1: Brand + NAP -->
      <div class="footer__brand">
        <span class="footer__logo">Abogados en CDMX</span>
        <p class="footer__nap">
          Abogados en CDMX es un despacho jurídico ubicado en Guanajuato 224, Colonia Roma Norte, Alcaldía Cuauhtémoc, C.P. 06700, Ciudad de México. Atendemos de lunes a viernes de 9:00 a 18:00 hrs.
        </p>
        <p class="footer__contact-line">
          <a href="tel:+525564655501">55 6465 5501</a> · <a href="mailto:contacto@abogadosencdmx.com">contacto@abogadosencdmx.com</a>
        </p>
        <div class="footer__social">
          <a href="https://facebook.com/abogadosencdmx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Facebook de Abogados en CDMX" class="footer__social-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/abogadosencdmx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Instagram de Abogados en CDMX" class="footer__social-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/abogadosencdmx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn de Abogados en CDMX" class="footer__social-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 2: Especialidades -->
      <nav class="footer__nav" aria-label="Especialidades">
        <h3 class="footer__heading">Especialidades</h3>
        <ul class="footer__menu">
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-familiar-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Familiar</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-penal-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Penal</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-civil-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Civil</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-corporativo-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Corporativo</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-inmobiliario-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Inmobiliario</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-migratorio-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Migratorio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/especialidades/derecho-laboral-cdmx" class="footer__link">Derecho Laboral</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <!-- Col 3: Links de interés -->
      <nav class="footer__nav" aria-label="Links de interés">
        <h3 class="footer__heading">Links de Interés</h3>
        <ul class="footer__menu">
          <li><a href="/especialidades" class="footer__link">Especialidades</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="footer__link">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/equipo-legal-cdmx" class="footer__link">Equipo Legal</a></li>
          <li><a href="/asesoria-inicial" class="footer__link">Asesoría Inicial</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calcular-pension-alimenticia" class="footer__link">Calculadora de Pensión</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calcular-finiquito" class="footer__link">Calculadora de Finiquito</a></li>
          <li><a href="/calcular-liquidacion-laboral" class="footer__link">Calculadora de Liquidación</a></li>
          <li><a href="/preguntas-frecuentes" class="footer__link">Preguntas Frecuentes</a></li>
          <li><a href="/aviso-de-privacidad" class="footer__link">Aviso de Privacidad</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <!-- Col 4: Horario -->
      <div class="footer__hours">
        <h3 class="footer__heading">Horario de Atención</h3>
        <p class="footer__hours-text">Lunes a viernes<br>9:00 — 18:00 hrs</p>
        <a href="/asesoria-inicial" class="btn-primary-wrap" style="margin-top:20px;">
          <span class="btn-primary" style="font-size:14px;padding:12px 24px;">Agendar cita →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer__bottom">
      <p>© 2026 Abogados en CDMX. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer { padding: 80px 0 0; }
  .footer__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
  .footer__logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; color: var(--color-white);
    display: block; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .footer__nap { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer__contact-line { font-size: 14px; }
  .footer__contact-line a { color: var(--color-secondary); }
  .footer__contact-line a:hover { color: var(--color-white); }

  .footer__social { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .footer__social-link {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .footer__social-link:hover {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  .footer__social-link svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }

  .footer__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .footer__menu { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .footer__link { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 15px; transition: color var(--transition); }
  .footer__link:hover { color: var(--color-secondary); }

  .footer__hours-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }

  .footer__bottom {
    padding: 24px 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .footer__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 479px) {
    .footer__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
  }
</style>
